{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <img src=\"https://cdn3.am730.com.hk/processed/2026-04/1027557/block/singleImage/3069199/df/01KQ9W2R2H2P5D6C86PBX4RDWW.jpg?updatedAt=1777374212\" alt=\"Byd\">\n    <p>比亞迪首季純利40.84億元，少賺55%。</p>\n    <img src=\"/assets/v2/img/ui/amlogo_grey_600_500.png\" alt=\"adblk4\">\n    <p>比亞迪(1211)公布2026年首季度報告。期內，集團錄得營業收入1502.25億人民幣(下同)，按年減少11.82%；純利40.84億元，按年下跌55.38%。基本每股收益0.448元。</p>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-28T14:33:06.348220+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":116,"images":2,"source":"am730","fallback":"none"}}